&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;The
proposal, by reason of scale and design, would be an undesirable
addition which would not provide an acceptable level of internal amenity space, failing to meet the requirements of the Nationally Described Space Standards.
As such, it would not provide an acceptable quality of accommodation, having a harmful impact on
the amenity of future occupiers. The proposal thus fails to accord
with the following policies which seek to ensure development proposals protect
residential amenity and provide a suitable quality of accommodation:&lt;/p&gt;

